cast.overview: Robert McCall finds himself at home in Southern Italy but he discovers his friends are under the control of local crime bosses. As events turn deadly, McCall knows what he has to do: become his friends' protector by taking on the mafia.
cast.title: The Equalizer 3

details.biography: Sonia Ben Ammar, also credited as Sonia Ammar, is a French-Tunisian model, singer, and actress, who is signed with IMG Models. She has appeared on several magazine covers, including Vanity Fair and L'Officiel. Ben Ammar released her debut extended play Sonia to positive reviews from critics.
details.name: Sonia Ammar
